A haunting close-up portrait of a woman draped in black lace with vivid crimson embroidery. The lace falls in intricate floral patterns over her face, partially concealing one eye while framing the other — a pale, unblinking eye that stares out with piercing intensity. Her skin is ghostly white, contrasting sharply with the deep red makeup smeared like blood across her eyelid, cheek, and temple, as if claw marks have been raked down her face. The mood is tense, intimate, and almost predatory, evoking gothic romance and supernatural menace.
